Library System
This is a simple Python project that models a library system. It consists of two classes: Book and Library.

Classes

1. Book
   This class represents a book and contains the following attributes:

title: The title of the book.
author: The author of the book.
ISBN: The ISBN of the book.

2. Library
   This class represents a library and includes the following functionalities:

add_book(book): Adds a Book object to the library's book list.
remove_book(book): Removes a Book object from the library's book list.
display_books(): Displays the details (title, author, and ISBN) of the books available in the library.
